{"id": "1423287753302343700", "channel_id": "1423287753302343700", "type": 0, "author_id": "705407952575529022", "author_name": "water_heart", "author_bot": false, "content": "簡單來說\n隊伍強效：43.2% （向上取整44%）\n寧妃攜帶鎖鏈 （基礎傷害提高40%）\n夜潮基傷：90\n夜潮成長：15\n90（基傷）×144%（強效）×140%（鎖鏈）\n=181.44 （向上取整182傷）\n\n這時候打出一張症狀\n觸發夜潮的傷害成長\n有時候計算公式為\n90（基傷）×144%（強效）×140%（鎖鏈）+15（成長）\n=197\n\n有時候計算公式為\n［90（基傷）+15（成長）］×144%（強效）×140%（鎖鏈）\n=211.68 （向上取整212）", "timestamp": "2025-10-02T12:37:23.795000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🛐", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}], "attachments": [{"id": "1423287753595949116", "filename": "Screenshot_2025-10-02-19-54-12-765_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 231313, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1423287753302343700/1423287753595949116/Screenshot_2025-10-02-19-54-12-765_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg?ex=69cbc003&is=69ca6e83&hm=28a6779beceb6b570d6252d7bf3cb43311398610242c672710cd60d74b7d1c48&"}, {"id": "1423287754128756797", "filename": "Screenshot_2025-10-02-20-25-05-539_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 233996, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1423287753302343700/1423287754128756797/Screenshot_2025-10-02-20-25-05-539_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg?ex=69cbc003&is=69ca6e83&hm=ea0ffe989332cccff56e46e87e8be2e048ab58b9eb8fc9a21d1c333148b55b3e&"}, {"id": "1423287754615160954", "filename": "Screenshot_2025-10-02-19-54-18-682_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk-1.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 226284, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1423287753302343700/1423287754615160954/Screenshot_2025-10-02-19-54-18-682_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk-1.jpg?ex=69cbc004&is=69ca6e84&hm=5b695439c444aeabe99fdacb392b912ff58b43cdd2e747e65887eff9ded64510&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1423287753302343700", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」寧妃，夜潮，BUG", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288